            <title>[LU-11758] remove assertion from osp_statfs()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11758</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sequence can&apos;t be changed or overflowed in case of IDIF.&lt;br/&gt;
Thus don&apos;t tigger kernel panic for below case:&lt;br/&gt;
last_created &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x100000001:0x15:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, next_fid &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x100000000:0xfffffff6:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
The same assertion that excepts IDIFs exists in osp_fid_diff.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
